SciMed Life Systems Inc said&lt;Advanced Cardiovascular Systems Inc> is suing it for patentinfringement.    The company said the suit involves a patent for a vascularguiding catheter assembly and a vascular dilating catheterassembly.    SciMed said the suit is without merit and it has turned thematter over to its attorneys.    It added that the lawsuit will not affect the negotiationson the merger transaction with Bristol-Meyers Co &lt;BMY>,announced Monday. Reuter&#3;